**Orion the Hunter** — Three bright stars form his belt (Alnitak, Alnilam, Mintaka). Betelgeuse glows red at his shoulder. Rigel blazes blue-white at his foot.

- 🌟 = named star of magnitude ≤ 2.0
- ✧ = variable or notable star

