**Taurus the Bull** flanks Orion to the northwest. The Pleiades (Seven Sisters) cluster marks his shoulder. Aldebaran, the red eye of the bull, burns fiercely.

- 💫 = the Pleiades open cluster (M45)
- The V-shape of stars is the Hyades cluster — the bull's face

